"Sleep well to-night. At three to-morrow the diligence
will start for Bukov ina; a place on it is kept for you. At the Borgo
Pass my carriage will await you and will bring you to me. I trust that
your journ ey from London has been a happy one, and that you will
enjoy your stay in my beautiful land. “Your friend,
