deeps, far down in the bottomless blue, rushed mighty leviathans, sword-fish ,
and sharks; and these were the strong, troubled, murderous thinkings of the
masculine sea. But though thus contrasting within, the contrast was only in shades and
shadows without; those two seemed one; it was only the sex, as it were, that
